CPST the worlds leading clean technology manufacturer of microturbine energy systems announced today that Lone Star Power Solutions its exclusive Distributor for Texas Arizona and the Gulf States signed another 3 megawatt MW Factory Protection Plan FPP longterm service contract in the Eagle Ford Shale Basin in South Texas This new contract adds to their already signed 12 MWs of FPP contracts previously secured in the same shale region during March of 2019
